<h2 class="sectionedit1"><a name="setlocale" id="setlocale">setlocale</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
Синтаксис:

</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp"><span class="co2">#include &lt;clocale&gt;</span>
<span class="kw4">char</span> <span class="sy2">*</span>setlocale<span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">int</span> category, <span class="kw4">const</span> <span class="kw4">char</span> <span class="sy2">*</span> locale <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>

Аргумент <code>category</code> может принимать следующие значения:
</p>
<div class="table sectionedit2"><table class="inline">
	<tr class="row0">
		<th class="col0 leftalign"> Значение    </th><th class="col1 leftalign"> Описание                                                                                                                    </th>
	</tr>
	<tr class="row1">
		<td class="col0 leftalign"> LC_ALL      </td><td class="col1 leftalign"> All of the locale                                                                                                           </td>
	</tr>
	<tr class="row2">
		<td class="col0 leftalign"> LC_TIME     </td><td class="col1 leftalign"> Date and time formatting                                                                                                    </td>
	</tr>
	<tr class="row3">
		<td class="col0 leftalign"> LC_NUMERIC  </td><td class="col1 leftalign"> Number formatting                                                                                                           </td>
	</tr>
	<tr class="row4">
		<td class="col0 leftalign"> LC_COLLATE  </td><td class="col1 leftalign"> String collation and regular expression matching                                                                            </td>
	</tr>
	<tr class="row5">
		<td class="col0 leftalign"> LC_CT    </td><td class="col1"> Regular expression matching, conversion, case-sensitive comparison, wide character functions, and character classification. </td>
	</tr>
	<tr class="row6">
		<td class="col0"> LC_MESSAGES </td><td class="col1 leftalign"> For natural language messages                                                                                               </td>
	</tr>
</table></div>
<!-- EDIT2 TABLE [229-1235] -->
</div>
